{"tid":533092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿部君做了雙面間諜（Double agent）","createTime":"2018-01-18T12:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T08:36:04.000Z","uid":7123,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"acb6eb923c14d81c6b506833900e71f39cd871d4","tid":533092,"uid":7123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T12:46:36.000Z","msg":"今日頭條報道曾任中情局（CIA）特工的港人懷疑洩密，並成為中國間諜，將線人絕密資料交給中方。據專門報道名貴拍賣的媒體《The Value》引述「可靠消息」報道，該名雙面間諜受僱於香港佳士得，為亞洲區保安主管。本報翻查資料，找到涉案特工相片和片段，他的身材健壯、瀏海有點凌亂、片中神情冷靜。<br />\n<br />\n這名53歲疑犯名為Jerry Chun Shing Lee（音譯為李振成），曾在去年9月1日佳士得香港《柯德莉夏萍私人珍藏》媒體預覽時現身，當時身穿藍色襯衣和擔任保安工作，徐徐經過柯德莉夏萍經典波點裙櫥窗外。佳士得發言人今日向《蘋果》回覆稱，該僱員在過去20個月在該拍賣行工作，主要負責佳士得設施和員工的保安工作，<br />\n<br />\n李振成除了是港人，亦是美籍歸化公民，1994至2007年在CIA擔任個案專員，負責招聘、管理線人工作，2007年離開CIA後定居本港，其後在佳士得工作，不時往來港美兩地。他周一晚乘搭國泰航空客機從香港飛抵紐約甘迺迪機場後被捕。<br />\n<br />\n佳士得回應稱，確認暫停僱用一名香港的僱員，該僱員現正接受刑事調查。該調查的重點是在他未受僱於佳士得以前。該僱員在過去20個月在本公司的工作，主要負責佳士得設施和員工的保安，其職責與數據安全和資訊科技沒有任何聯繫。佳士得並沒有涉及事件，對後續調查沒有附加評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10156383655227448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fposts%2F10156383655227448&d=6AgurqSXUKIqbV6VfhvAGtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=37e877f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10156383655227448</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/18/204449_3d09ac7e10a3dc2c70d411bc8d3083aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F18%2F204449_3d09ac7e10a3dc2c70d411bc8d3083aa.jpg&h=ddb7023e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/18/204450_5694236a950fc2f6a67c4f24c4cac073.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F18%2F204450_5694236a950fc2f6a67c4f24c4cac073.jpg&h=d4e0ce29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.thevalue.com/articles/cia-ex-officer-jerry-lee-chun-shing-spying-suspected-compromising-chinese-informants-arrested-christies-hong-kong-exclusive-photo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.thevalue.com%2Farticles%2Fcia-ex-officer-jerry-lee-chun-shing-spying-suspected-compromising-chinese-informants-arrested-christies-hong-kong-exclusive-photo&d=6AgurqSXUKIqbV6VfhvAGtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=a0b48075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.thevalue.com/articles/cia-ex-officer-jerry-lee-chun-shing-spying-suspected-compromising-chinese-informants-arrested-christies-hong-kong-exclusive-photo</a>"},{"pid":"a4c2242883fb3a84286ea63aeabfd8fc132adebc","tid":533092,"uid":7123,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T12:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img31.mtime.cn/pi/2012/06/04/094510.62452323.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg31.mtime.cn%2Fpi%2F2012%2F06%2F04%2F094510.62452323.jpg&h=6de5d529&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcda81b2b0659a1892679bf9aa35c567b2411e02","tid":533092,"uid":104793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"頂, 佢真係好靚仔, 之前上佳士得可能見過佢, 真係水都出埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d7295b4333764b0f0c0c1160dff036da87f9d5","tid":533092,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fcda81b2b0659a1892679bf9aa35c567b2411e02","tid":533092,"uid":104793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"頂, 佢真係好靚仔, 之前上佳士得可能見過佢, 真係水都出埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T14:01:28.000Z","msg":"五十幾歲都咁型"},{"pid":"5f2ccff3cbf974c2099902061e23e0b529a8e592","tid":533092,"uid":7123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>頂, 佢真係好靚仔, 之前上佳士得可能見過佢, 真係水都出埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>五十幾歲都咁型</blockquote><br />\n真係好少人可以keep得咁好"